{
  "stem": "7069.4",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But some of them could hardly walk.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "You could see.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And of course, these eventually then, the guy went like this.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They went to the, to the Auschwitz side.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we went to the Birkenau side, which was the work camp of the Auschwitz camp.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And so we were in this camp then.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We, we got in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "By the way, this was, the whole thing took almost all day long.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We got in.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And we started-- we stopped in front of a big barrack, which turned out to be a shower room.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We were ordered to shed our clothes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And we were taken into that room.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And we had a wonderful shower.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "But by the way, the suitcases that we had-- that they took away from us right away when we, when we entered the train, they said, you will get your suitcase afterwards.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "It was like as if you go to a spa, you know, where they deliver the suitcase after.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "They were taken away.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "We never saw that again, of course.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And so now here we were in a shower.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And we were ordered to get out of the shower.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And there was a long line of tables with these prisoner's striped clothes.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And we were moving towards that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And the guy with his megaphone, oh, wait a minute.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Hold everything.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "We are not ready for that yet.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "First of all, your hair has to be shorn.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "So we stood, had to stand in line, and all our hair was shorn, in fact, all over the body.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And then when this was done, we thought, now we can get our clothes.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "He says, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "Wait a minute.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "There is one more thing that we have to do before you get to the camp.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
